Convenient, and a good deal on the sale items.
Not so sold on the standard prices for most of my staples, however, and the aisles could certainly be cleaner.

I use the bakery and deli at this store often for food for business meetings and trainings.
The bakery makes great cookie trays, not the type you expect from a chain grocery store.
Their fresh baked fresh daily rolls and buns are the best.
The deli has freshly made fruit and veggie trays that are reasonable priced and nicely done.

